reviewText: 1940 audio and video,waste of your money!!!!
a lot of stuff repeated. footage I had already seen. really not worth the price I payed!

Marvelous bargain!  You have probably seen them all.  If you, like me, re-visit from time to time, This collection is must.  Yes, I too wish the Victor At Sea series would be remastered to at least mute the blaring musical background.
A lot of documentaries and superior video!
if you want just the video this works out OK. There are no booklet/notes/special-features , but then again this is a rather low price for all the discs.
